      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span><br>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/f0d674be287c96be7066ab5e4e75b0fb_949722499035839394.png",
                "id": "talent86402",
                "key": "Card Force Translocation",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Card Force Translocation"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>, memanggil <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Grin-Malkin Hat</span>, dan mendapatkan 1 lapis <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span>.</p><p>Jika Karakter ini memiliki 6 poin HP atau lebih, maka akan mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> terhadap diri sendiri.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Prop Surplus</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span> dapat ditumpuk hingga 3 lapis.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter menggunakan Bewildering Lights:</span> Setiap lapisan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span> mengakibatkan DMG +1. Setelah penghitungan skill selesai, akan mengonsumsi seluruh lapisan<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> Prop Surplus</span>, setiap lapisan akan memulihkan 1 poin HP Karakter.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/67d6f9d70e695a791caa42953d11e1e3_2819657223384818004.png",
                "id": "talent85446",
                "key": "Prop Arrow",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Prop Arrow"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/053697dd2072f984e7e9b4e118b3dec9_1239886188388392612.png",
                "id": "talent73448",
                "key": "Bewildering Lights",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Bewildering Lights"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> Pyro DMG</span>, memanggil <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Grin-Malkin Hat</span>, dan mendapatkan 1 lapis <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Prop Surplus</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span> dapat ditumpuk hingga 3 lapis.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter menggunakan Bewildering Lights:</span> Setiap lapisan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span> mengakibatkan DMG +1. Setelah penghitungan skill selesai, akan mengonsumsi seluruh lapisan<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> Prop Surplus</span>, setiap lapisan akan memulihkan 1 poin HP Karakter.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/1f6d82b825fc55a454fe56d6bb68239e_593383234557440599.png",
                "id": "talent52784",
                "key": "Wondrous Trick: Miracle Parade",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Wondrous Trick: Miracle Parade"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Panggilan </span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 1</span> (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 lapis)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5512374365465818998.png",
                "id": "talent90893",
                "key": "Grin-Malkin Hat",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/0ed08f29bee33744061b306f8acdaf20_8599032717937387498.png",
                "title": "Grin-Malkin Hat"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Pyro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini, target berganti ke Karakter selanjutnya secara paksa</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] yang mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG di akhir Ronde (Jumlah penggunaan sekali, maksimum 2 tumpukan)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_1870045108823632159.png",
                "id": "talent76024",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Piercing DMG</span></strong></p><p>Piercing DMG tidak dapat dipengaruhi oleh Bonus DMG apa pun, namun tidak dapat ditahan oleh efek seperti Perisai atau kekebalan DMG.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3958660588654313334.png",
